            </p>
          </li>
          <li><a class="text-gray-200 hover:underline transition duration-150 ease-in-out text-sm"
              href="/privacy-policy">privacy
              policy</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="py-4 md:py-8">
      <div class="text-sm text-gray-400 mr-4">
        Copyright &copy; 2022 Decentree software s.r.o. All rights reserved.
